A new note on picking locks, though.<br>
There's several doors that can only be picked if you have a skill of 201 or higher (notably, the bank vault in Freeport, among others). But you can't get higher than a 200 until you reach level 51. So at level 39, you're stuck at 200 for the next 12 levels.<br>
